<div class="service_divider"></div>
<h2 class="service_title">
	<span>TAKE THE OPPORTUNITY TO RAISE MONEY OR INVEST ON PROJECTS</span></h2>
<h3 class="service_subtitle">Mobilize our network to spread the word of mouth about your fundraising campaign<br/>and gauge one more step towards your company growth.</h3>
<h3 class="service_subtitle">How does it work?</h3>
<div class="service_container">
	<div class="service_desc">
		<p>
		1 - Fill out an online form detailing the fundraising goal and your investment needs<br/>
		2 - We will verify your profile and documents and connect you to the investors more compatible with you<br/>
		3 - To any need along the way (legal, communicational, managerial or administrative) our partners and experts can be connected to you</p>
	</div>
</div>
